text: Ibrahim Ismail Chundrigar (, April 15, 1898 - March 13, 1968), commonly known as I. I. Chundrigar, was Prime Minister of Pakistan for about 2 months from October 17, 1957 to December 16, 1957. Category:1898 births Category:1968 deaths Category:Prime ministers of Pakistan
title: Ibrahim Ismail Chundrigar
